title: Tab for 'Not yet Voted' on vote.sav3.org
body:
Since proposals are not not always approved in the same order, it is possible that long pending proposals get overlooked once approved.

On vote.sav3.org add a tab for 'Not yet Voted' proposals so that you can easily see what proposals are pending for you to vote on.
choices: Continue manually checking each proposal to find those not yet voted on
author: 0x4d28975B4Ed2a1a9A00C657f28344DCe37EE0Ac6
